videos.headline: Delvin Cook to the house for Florida State
videos.description: It takes all of two plays before Florida State's Delvin Cook puts his stamp on the game with a 75-yard touchdown to give the Seminoles the early lead.

videos.headline: Dabo Swinney's massive dance party
videos.description: After clinching a spot in the ACC Championship game, Clemson coach Dabo Swinney shows off his best dance moves to his team.
